<title>Shortcut keys</title>

<p>This page provides an overview of keyboard shortcuts that can help you
use <app>Evolution</app> more efficiently.</p>

<note style="tip">
<p>In addition to the shortcuts listed below, you can also use accelerators to navigate with the keyboard.</p> 
<p>Hold down the <key>Alt</key> key to reveal <em>accelerators</em>:
underlined letters on menu items, buttons, and other controls. Press
<key>Alt</key> plus the underlined letter to activate a control, just
as if you had clicked on it.</p>
</note>


