    </p></td>
    <td><p>Jump to next message.</p></td>
  </tr>
  <tr xml:id="mail-arrow-up">
    <td><p>
      <key>↑</key>
    </p></td>
    <td><p>Jump to previous message.</p></td>
  </tr>
  <tr xml:id="mail-dot">
    <td><p>
      <key>.</key> or <key>]</key>
    </p></td>
